name: Genomation
body:
### Welcome to Genomation.
This is an R package that contains a collection of tools for visualizing and analyzing genome-wide data sets.

### Authors and Contributors
Vedran Franke (@frenkiboy) and Altuna Akalin (@al2na) authored this package.

### Support or Contact
@frenkiboy or @al2na
